304
01:36:05,708 --> 01:36:06,791
Even you?

305
01:36:09,750 --> 01:36:10,875
It's shocking.

306
01:36:19,916 --> 01:36:26,166
I warned you not to get over-familiar
with that man. You ignored me.

307
01:36:27,708 --> 01:36:30,375
